name: Type Faster
description:
Type Faster is a typing game, where you can learn to type fast and avoid errors.

You can play different genres like "usual words",  "names",  "passwords" etc.

Online ranking is now avaiable, rank against your friends and other players to see whos better!

There will be achievments, and more genres in the future. You can leave suggestions for genres down below! (still in development)

Good luck while playing and have fun!

Community: https://discord.gg/Yku4xyN
